"title": "5763: attitudes, positive to God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5763: attitudes, positive to god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture identifies a range of positive attitudes towards God, which believers are encouraged to adopt.</p>\n<h2>Trust</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:5\">PRO 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:7\">PSA 20:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:1-Ps25:2\">PSA 25:1–25:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:4\">PSA 40:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:11\">PSA 56:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a></p>\n<h2>Faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:10\">MAT 8:10</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:9\">LUK 7:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:2\">MAT 9:2</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:5\">MRK 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:20\">LUK 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:1-Heb11:39\">HEB 11:1–11:39</a></p>\n<h2>Hope</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job13:15\">JOB 13:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:5\">PSA 25:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:31\">ISA 40:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:7\">MIC 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:18\">ROM 4:18</a></p>\n<h2>Love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:6\">DEU 30:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:1\">PSA 18:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:1\">PSA 116:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:15-John21:17\">JHN 21:15–21:17</a></p>\n<h2>Holiness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:14\">HEB 12:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:6\">DEU 7:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:1-Deut14:2\">DEU 14:1–14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:7-1Cor5:8\">1CO 5:7–5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:2\">COL 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>Awesome respect</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:13\">ECC 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12-Deut10:13\">DEU 10:12–10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">PRO 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:10\">PRO 9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:22\">JER 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">ACT 9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:7\">REV 14:7</a></p>\n<h2>Repentance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:10\">2CO 7:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:6\">JOB 42:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:6\">EZK 14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:30\">ACT 17:30</a></p>\n<h2>Humility</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:2\">ISA 66:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:21\">EZR 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:10\">JAS 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:6\">1PE 5:6</a></p>\n<h2>Self-denial</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a></p>\n<h2>Submission</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:7\">JAS 4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:21\">JOB 22:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:7\">ROM 8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:3\">ROM 10:3</a></p>\n<h2>Thankfulness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:18\">1TH 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:34\">1CH 16:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:18\">PSA 35:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:4\">PSA 100:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:19\">MAT 14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:20\">EPH 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6\">PHP 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:7\">COL 2:7</a></p>\n<h2>Praise</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:15\">HEB 13:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:11\">EZR 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:1-Ps148:5\">PSA 148:1–148:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:1-Ps150:6\">PSA 150:1–150:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:10\">ISA 42:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:3\">ISA 61:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:46-Acts2:47\">ACT 2:46–2:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:13\">JAS 5:13</a></p>\n<h2>Prayerfulness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:13\">JAS 5:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:23\">MAT 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:41\">MAT 26:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26\">ROM 8:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:17\">1TH 5:17</a></p>\n<h2>Reverence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:7\">PSA 5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:15\">NEH 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:5\">MAL 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:2\">MAL 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:21\">EPH 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:28\">HEB 12:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:1-1Pet3:2\">1PE 3:1–3:2</a></p>\n<h2>Watchfulness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:2\">COL 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:37-Luke12:38\">LUK 12:37–12:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:6-1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:6–5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8\">1PE 5:8</a></p>",
